@startuml Android版AI问答系统顺序图
!theme plain

actor User as 用户
participant "MainActivity" as MainAct
participant "TabbedActivity" as TabAct
participant "ChatFragment" as ChatFrag
participant "ServiceManager" as ServiceMgr
participant "AIService" as AIService
participant "ApiService" as ApiService
participant "MessageAdapter" as MsgAdapter
participant "StorageService" as StorageSvc
participant "TextToSpeech" as TTS

== 应用启动流程 ==
autonumber 1
用户 -> MainAct: 启动应用
activate MainAct
MainAct -> MainAct: onCreate()
MainAct -> TabAct: 启动TabbedActivity
deactivate MainAct

activate TabAct
TabAct -> TabAct: onCreate()
TabAct -> TabAct: initializeServices()
TabAct -> ServiceMgr: getInstance()
activate ServiceMgr
ServiceMgr --> TabAct: 返回ServiceManager实例
deactivate ServiceMgr
TabAct -> ServiceMgr: setApiService(new ApiService(this))
TabAct -> ServiceMgr: setStorageService(new StorageService(this))
TabAct -> TabAct: 设置ViewPager和Adapter
TabAct --> User: 显示主界面
deactivate TabAct

== 文本问答流程 ==
autonumber 10
用户 -> ChatFrag: 输入问题并点击发送
activate ChatFrag
ChatFrag -> ChatFrag: sendMessage()
ChatFrag -> ChatFrag: 创建用户消息
ChatFrag -> MsgAdapter: addMessage(userMessage)
activate MsgAdapter
MsgAdapter -> MsgAdapter: notifyItemInserted()
MsgAdapter --> ChatFrag: 更新UI完成
deactivate MsgAdapter

ChatFrag -> ServiceMgr: getApiService()
activate ServiceMgr
ServiceMgr --> ChatFrag: 返回ApiService实例
deactivate ServiceMgr

ChatFrag -> AIService: getAnswer(question, model)
activate AIService
AIService -> ApiService: getAnswer(question, model, callback)
activate ApiService

ApiService -> ApiService: 选择AI模型
alt model = ZHIPU
    ApiService -> ApiService: callZhipuAPI(question)
else model = DEEPSEEK
    ApiService -> ApiService: callDeepSeekAPI(question)
end

ApiService -> ApiService: makeApiCall(url, requestBody, callback)
ApiService -> ApiService: 发送HTTP请求
ApiService --> AIService: 返回AI回答
deactivate ApiService

AIService --> ChatFrag: 返回AI回答
deactivate AIService

ChatFrag -> ChatFrag: 创建AI回复消息
ChatFrag -> MsgAdapter: addMessage(aiMessage)
activate MsgAdapter
MsgAdapter -> MsgAdapter: notifyItemInserted()
MsgAdapter --> ChatFrag: 更新UI完成
deactivate MsgAdapter

ChatFrag -> StorageSvc: saveMessages(messages)
activate StorageSvc
StorageSvc -> StorageSvc: 序列化消息到JSON
StorageSvc -> StorageSvc: 保存到本地文件
StorageSvc --> ChatFrag: 保存完成
deactivate StorageSvc

deactivate ChatFrag

== 语音合成流程 ==
autonumber 30
用户 -> ChatFrag: 点击消息的语音按钮
activate ChatFrag
ChatFrag -> ChatFrag: speak(messageContent)
ChatFrag -> TTS: speak(text, queueMode, params)
activate TTS
TTS -> TTS: 初始化语音合成引擎
TTS -> TTS: 合成语音
TTS --> ChatFrag: 播放语音
deactivate TTS
deactivate ChatFrag

== 消息历史加载流程 ==
autonumber 40
用户 -> ChatFrag: 打开聊天界面
activate ChatFrag
ChatFrag -> ChatFrag: onViewCreated()
ChatFrag -> ServiceMgr: getStorageService()
activate ServiceMgr
ServiceMgr --> ChatFrag: 返回StorageService实例
deactivate ServiceMgr

ChatFrag -> StorageSvc: loadMessages()
activate StorageSvc
StorageSvc -> StorageSvc: 从本地文件读取
StorageSvc -> StorageSvc: 反序列化JSON为消息列表
StorageSvc --> ChatFrag: 返回消息列表
deactivate StorageSvc

ChatFrag -> MsgAdapter: setMessages(messages)
activate MsgAdapter
MsgAdapter -> MsgAdapter: notifyDataSetChanged()
MsgAdapter --> ChatFrag: 更新UI完成
deactivate MsgAdapter
deactivate ChatFrag

== 清空消息流程 ==
autonumber 50
用户 -> ChatFrag: 点击清空按钮
activate ChatFrag
ChatFrag -> MsgAdapter: clearMessages()
activate MsgAdapter
MsgAdapter -> MsgAdapter: 清空消息列表
MsgAdapter -> MsgAdapter: notifyDataSetChanged()
MsgAdapter --> ChatFrag: 更新UI完成
deactivate MsgAdapter

ChatFrag -> StorageSvc: clearMessages()
activate StorageSvc
StorageSvc -> StorageSvc: 删除本地消息文件
StorageSvc --> ChatFrag: 清空完成
deactivate StorageSvc
deactivate ChatFrag

@enduml